query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind not in ('cast','complete','crew') AND it.info not in ('keywords','countries','LD analog left','book','genres','runtimes','books','LD review','LD number of sides','rating','mpaa','death date','plot','color info','bottom 10 rank','release dates','production process protocol','birth name') AND (an.name like '%h%' OR an.name like '%P%' OR an.name like '%H%') AND (k.keyword like '%survival%' OR k.keyword like '%passion%' OR k.keyword like '%horror%') AND (chn.name like '%Aragorn%' OR chn.name like '%John Wick%' OR chn.name like '%Rocky Balboa%') AND mi.info in ('Mandarin','Maori','Indonesian','German','Polish','Russian','Japanese','Swedish','Persian','Hebrew','Flemish') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','cast','complete+verified') AND (rt.role like '%BEF%' OR rt.role like '%Famous Black Raincoat%' OR rt.role like '%Samson Yee%' OR rt.role like '%MF%')
